Meanwhile, B2B fintech <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/evenfinancial/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">Even Financial</a> posts hiring and company news on LinkedIn to position itself as a leader in its industry and help open the door for top talent.

